data.description: Major price adjustment!  Don't miss this spacious and well maintained home!   Hard wood floors in the Living Room and hall.  Tile flooring accents the updated Kitchen with newer stainless steel appliances. Five bedrooms that are located with 3 up and 2 down. The lower level Family Room is perfect for entertaining or just relaxing. Electric outlets have been updated throughout.  Spacious yard with utility shed.  Plenty of off street parking. Just minutes from the location of the new GOOGLE Data Center coming soon on Rathmell Road!!PLEASE see A2A remarks!
